Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  去练习咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  马上就要到文化祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别像去年那样努力过头  结果感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在每天都吃桔子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手都发黄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于活动室…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不能用？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐室不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上无人的教室里发出嘀嗒嘀嗒的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我没事的  请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得奇怪就调查了一下  发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是天花板漏水了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那是活动室下面的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能换掉供水管道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但管道要穿过活动室  所以就不让进了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离文化祭都不到一个月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之乐器都拿到外面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有乌龟也拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猪鼻龟啦  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室因为要进行管道施工而用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法喝茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据预测  施工好像要10天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说在这段期间里没法在活动室里练习吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在别的地方练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹奏乐部和合唱部使用的第二音乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去交涉看看能不能借用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定你们已经忘了  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是吹奏乐部的顾问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止入内的话  里面到底是怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看吗  要去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～刚才你那自信满满的样子算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要在哪里练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在教室里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  要在这里练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出很大声音会给别人添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们就稍微练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  这里是我们的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不用客气  不用拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是把鞋脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  开始吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就从「咖喱」开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在在讨论文化祭的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的声音有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太吵了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  该说对不起的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猪放在教室里不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子乖呀  快快睡啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:27.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（童谣「江戸子守唄」：催眠曲中的代表曲，实际曲名不明）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里能让我们用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点窄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  光是移动乐器就已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不适合在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里全是运动部的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要开始练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  不由自主地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪意外地喜欢看体育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT  FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉气势很不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也热血而充满根性地演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音  FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音  FIGHT  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是这个气势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作不齐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很难集中精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大礼堂有演剧部在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋顶上有吟诗部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:06:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和和的座位  你坐下来也没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成「轻音部」  其实读作「双六」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（双六：凭骰子的点数抢先将全部棋子移入对方阵地的游戏）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到长袖和服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想说「起点」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没错  是「起点」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种很难理解的地方说错词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是流浪的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你们没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我会去找个能练习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经到离校时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能定下个安静的地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能吃到点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想的果然是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你词写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曲子的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲目完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然的曲子已经作好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌词我写了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  律却说不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散发甜味的点心之森里  和小鸟说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗  很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的恋情上点缀白和黑  就像熊猫一样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和企鹅跳舞跳舞跳舞之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个动物系列是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪一进入动物的话题就会得病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想化身成狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓我走吧狒狒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家都来作词看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这提议好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌词就这么否决了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～作为一个候补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么每个人都去作词  明天发表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待小梓的歌词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点兴奋不已了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…要取什么标题好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从标题开始作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫「心跳心跳量角器」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「书包是笨蛋」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是冷笑话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真点考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然讨论了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有轻音部能练习的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  怎么能这么干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑去问爵士研的活动室能借吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去了理科室  烹调室  会议室  甚至校长室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天就把高跟鞋磨坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活动室能用之前  先暂停集体练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要到文化祭了  不练习可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去借个出租工作室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租工作室？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要花很多钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  部费还有剩余
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律是个唯利是图的人真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到附近就有出租工作室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有卖拨片和贴纸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在这里填上负责人的姓名和住址
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  去写～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在第一次来的时候需要看下身份证明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份证明？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来证明！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的确是樱高轻音部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  用学生证什么的就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多招人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我们也来贴一张招收成员海报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别扯那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了…噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预想的还要小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么奢侈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子吗？不是镜子吗？就是镜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我背吉太的方式是不是太逊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总算发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面大镜子摆在这儿  下意识就这样了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能在演奏中审查自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你说要找插座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间内禁止饮食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我们知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  好像在看着我们一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真的哦  你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都泡好了  上外面喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～终于平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我们不是为了平静心灵才跑来租场地的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了这杯就去练习啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好利用这段时间  来发表一下写好的歌词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那从谁先开始呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐你竟然写好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我读了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米饭最好吃  配什么都香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面乌冬煎菜饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳水化合物与碳水化合物的梦幻联合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我觉得高潮部分的歌词很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四  吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日语发音首音与「五」相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带说一下标题是「米饭是菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒风凛冽冻骨寒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉江将犯人逼上了悬崖绝壁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健一先生  你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  驳回～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你这是歌词？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想试试以前没用过的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可不可以不读啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很没有自信的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读啦读啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直感受到你摇曳不定的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我  不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂小猪的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去重写
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那律写了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲑鱼子多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫猫睡过头…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都不太好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你写歌词呢歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪的写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「浣熊洗礼的恋爱」和「长颈鹿凛凛」你想看哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么一套？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  怎么还在搞这种事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧  来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有什么在闪哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么演出啊？特殊服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是结束时间通知…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪泡了茶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的最多的不是小唯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉工作室白借了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室不知道怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都去反而不知道那边的好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动室的施工已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预定快了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能回活动室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们夸张的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐器就都放上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我帮你们带到学校去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆送我回家啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上车～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了五个人上不来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～小心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这里好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能在这里练习  实在是该心怀感激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新认识了一遍对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用再四处晃来晃去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了！以后每天都来这里就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来弹一首！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下歌词了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  梨切好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部每个人都要写一份歌词上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也要写？好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「米饭是菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可大家的反响都不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很有独创性！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这梨好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今晚熬夜努力啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗？别太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？谢谢你  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋空空的～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作词还挺难的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯好像挺有自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我已经写好三首了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  非常押韵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是你写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧帮了一点点小忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯好像没睡好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在写歌词  没有好好睡成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别像去年那样弄感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  有桔子神保佑着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分你一点桔子神力吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忧感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别着急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是忧的话也是个大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…喝点茶吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好躺着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧倒是不太高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么唯啊  我们就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你们要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在的话  忧也不能好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在  姐姐你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧你是病人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  忧  我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事马上打电话给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随叫随到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我一个人没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而会担心传染感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我来做稀饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鸡蛋掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…担心地睡不着  可不睡又好不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…最珍视的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是伴随在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却当成理所当然  没有察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感觉好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀饭上放荷包蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（稀饭做好了  记得吃哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「U & I」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你我什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃你做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你我连道歉都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据投票结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定采用唯的歌词！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都被感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抱着「失去后才懂得珍惜」的心情去写的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是唯学姐写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是忧和活动室让你写出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～我的才能终于开花了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自夸了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌词…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  作两首行了吧  两首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  别说两首了  三首四首都听你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  其实我…要转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.81,0:23:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爸爸工作的关系  我要移居到伊尔库茨克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  无论如何都演不了的话我会重新考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:23:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔唔唔…


